<p>Rashere</p><br><hr></blockquote>I would say that just due to the design changes to the zone changed it from a raid zone to a XP zone.&nbsp; In the old zone, you had risks on porting up, on pathing, and on 2nd floor aggro to deal with.&nbsp; That is one hting that made Hate a dangerous place and that is gone now.<br><br>Also, the Skylance group instances (Library/Oubilette/Labratory) have their mobs flagged as riad mobs.&nbsp; This includes the mites in Oub.<br></div>
				
