<P><BR>Yeah, this one is a pain.&nbsp; Essentially, we flagged all NPCs in the LDoN raids to be raid NPCs.&nbsp; The ones you are seeing are NPCs that are shared across multiple LDoN adventures including the raid ones.&nbsp; To fix this, I have to dig through and figure out which ones are only in the raid and which aren't, then create new NPCs for the ones that are shared so that they aren't anymore.&nbsp; Very time consuming.</P>
